{"tid":2418091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女侍應被搜出雷射筆遭控 辯稱現場沒示威 官月底裁決","createTime":"2021-02-22T10:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T12:37:02.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0148417bd9ca0110db2cb2b70a670725633f36","tid":2418091,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:58:14.000Z","msg":"前年8月10日大埔反修例遊行，晚上演變成多區快閃示威，有示威者包圍馬鞍山警署。其間一名31歲女侍應被指以雷射筆照射警署平台上的警員，被控管有攻擊性器罪。她早前供稱購<span class=\"red\">買雷射筆打算回家與貓玩耍</span>，途經馬鞍山警署對開時使用過雷射筆「隨意轉咗個圈」，回家期間被截停。案件押後至3月29日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又強調，控罪所指的地方並非馬鞍山警署對開，現場不僅不是示威現場，控方所指有人用雷射筆照向警署事件亦已成過去式，被告不知警署三樓有警員站崗。即使藏有雷射筆，也並沒有如控方所稱的非法用途。而且被告當時沒有叫囂，僅有一個防毒面罩及泳鏡，望能裁定罪脫。"},{"pid":"3db9a53cf6e11fcdd4e21da72c7ae751bf5eb5c5","tid":2418091,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:58:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/OQYBWSQCU5DOFDZJAZY367YYZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FOQYBWSQCU5DOFDZJAZY367YYZY%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=c53970f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FOQYBWSQCU5DOFDZJAZY367YYZY%2F&h=0983c416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/OQYBWSQCU5DOFDZJAZY367YYZY/</a>"},{"pid":"31f15a63f2343404fe1eb62ebec4e4e62355d948","tid":2418091,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9904175b9e2feefb1c65d3e945d264cf58c8cca","tid":2418091,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b15ae3e9553a453eda2159f1abc18469e15